ED_Title: Notification by the Secretary-General under Article 12, paragraph 2, of the Charter of the United Nations
ED_DecisionText: At its 62nd plenary meeting, on 3 September 2020, the General Assembly took note of the note by the Secretary-General (A/74/300).
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the resumed part of the session will be contained in the official record of the GA (A/74/49 (Vol. III)) after editorial review.
